725777f-c.title: Queens: 109th Avenue - 130th Street
725777f-c.text:
One Hundred Ninth Ave., south side, in line of 130th and
131st Streets, showing the W. Jellinghaus house of 1860; also the
Ditmars Van Siclen farmhouse. His estate of fifty acres was sold
by his executors on February 1925 for '350,0O0. The outbuildings
are in the line of 131st Street. This is a set of three views.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
c
